WEBVTT

00:13:01.106 --> 00:13:03.087
And Fred,

00:13:03.111 --> 00:13:04.484
son of a preacher,

00:13:05.882 --> 00:13:08.344
looks up at Mabel, and he says,

00:13:08.368 --> 00:13:13.369
"But Mabel, didn't Jesus
die on the cross for our sins?

00:13:13.784 --> 00:13:15.326
Wasn't that a good outcome?

00:13:15.350 --> 00:13:18.742
Maybe this will be a good outcome.

00:13:18.766 --> 00:13:23.399
Maybe the death of Martin Luther King
will lead to a good outcome."

00:13:24.100 --> 00:13:26.374
And as Fred tells the story,

00:13:26.398 --> 00:13:30.140
he says that Mabel
put her hand over her mouth,